prodNameC: 拜爾斯達光學免疫法困難腸梭菌毒素A測定試劑
ingredientsDesc:
Reagent 1-11.2 mL:
Conjugate, contains buffered Anti-Clostridium difficile Toxin A antibody (murine) conjugated to Horseradish Peroxidase (HRP) in a bufered protein solution.
Wash Solution-125 mL:
buffered saline solution. 
Substrate-2.0 mL
Tetramethylbenzidine (TMB) and Hydrogen Peroxide (H2O2).
Test Devices-30 ea.
Surface coated with Anti-Clostridium difficile Toxin A antibody (rabbit).
Positive Control-1.0 mL
Purified Clostridium difficile Toxin A. 
Negative Control-1.0 mL
Buffered protein solution with detergent.
Extraction Tubes-30 ea.
Transfer Pipettes-30 ea.
Sampling Brushes-30 ea.
Dropper Bulb-1 ea.
applicantAddr: 新北市永和區中山路一段174號11樓
efficacy: 定性偵測人體糞便檢體中困難腸梭菌毒素A。
